fields.body: We’re kickin off this weekend RIGHT NOW. The main man TJR has just put out (2) phenomenal mixes for the masses, representing the electro edge and the funky fidgety techno side. In celebration of TJ performing @ ourVERSUS party tonight in Santa Monica, he has given us the exclusive unveiling of the track listing for his mysterious ‘Funky Tekno’ mix –  we’ll wait a second while you go “YESSSTTTTHHHHH.” Packed with staples from this madman’s DJ sets, you’re bound to find some gems in these track listings. TJR has huge releases forthcoming on Chris Lake’s Rising Musiclabel, along with support from the likes of Tiesto, Fatboy Slim, Chuckie, Benny Benassi, Dada Life, Calvin Harris, Steve Aoki and so many more…
fields.title: TJR – MIXTAPE DOUBLEHEADER + TONIGHT @ VERSUS!

fields.body: Kavinsky is Dark, orchestrated, and Dirty. Love the violins and heavy over-tones. Here’s the first teaser of his new album to be released soon in the new year. Don’t play this in your car, you’ll end up arrested.
fields.title: KAVINSKY – ROAD GAMES

fields.body: Rolling along into the new year, CONTROL brings you a colossal lineup this week @ the Avalon. We welcome back the breakbeat monster duo Stanton Warriors, along with big room terror Bassjackers all the way from the Netherlands.
fields.title: CONTROL (1/13) FT. STANTON WARRIORS, BASSJACKERS, CLOCKWORK

fields.body: This week marked a huge milestone for the ever-growing relationship between Dim Mak and GDD™. BONES began his residency at the famed Dim Mak Studios Tuesday weekly, and we’re keeping tonight as BONES.
fields.title: THE M MACHINE + BONES TONIGHT AT DRAI’S HOLLYWOOD!
